{"tid":461432,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"名古屋中部機場一問","createTime":"2017-11-07T14:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T12:58:22.000Z","uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bea15169d7808e07f2ae7d6258e283d12377debe","tid":461432,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"因為黎緊會係名古屋轉機 (內陸1710去新千歲) <br />\n想問下名古屋出境要幾耐到<br />\ngoogle左好似一般半個鐘就ok<br />\n我考慮緊坐早1個鐘垃圾快運UO1584 13:40到 定因航CX536 1455到 (兩者都有機會delay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n坐因航準時的話有2個鐘轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前一日下午有事做"},{"pid":"d44daf844b7638589624987f6e12aa09aab742ff","tid":461432,"uid":3739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"零晨機搭peach去大阪再搭新幹線上名古屋"},{"pid":"8182cee02a4e9e168756e770aa74d240acc46d1b","tid":461432,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>零晨機搭peach去大阪再搭新幹線上名古屋</blockquote><br />\n好似好浪費時間同金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432c71fbe7b98ed71ac2f1cb7d97ba0151ad948d","tid":461432,"uid":3739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>零晨機搭peach去大阪再搭新幹線上名古屋</blockquote><br />\n好似好浪費時間同金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n浪費得過你轉唔切機去北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真係好難講會唔會轉得切 佢一delay你就仆硬街<br />\n最安全又萬無一失既方法係大阪上去名古屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落機可以去黑門市場食早餐 心齋橋兜個圈先上新幹線都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61c9a1e7dc523819b225198754db4bc9deb1d87","tid":461432,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"暑假搭因航CX536轉同一班機, 因為預左轉機慢慢過關, 加上之前有班支那機, 用左75分鐘<br />\n出關上2層就check in<br />\n最後仲要delay 左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中部機場一過安檢就上機, 10分鐘都唔洗到閘口"},{"pid":"f15298ec8dd0769097decf92963f6c553fd91266","tid":461432,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暑假搭因航CX536轉同一班機, 因為預左轉機慢慢過關, 加上之前有班支那機, 用左75分鐘<br />\n出關上2層就check in<br />\n最後仲要delay 左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中部機場一過安檢就上機, 10分鐘都唔洗到閘口</blockquote><br />\ndelay係指因航定轉果班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48312767b321b36d3292297ab3327c4a34300ac9","tid":461432,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054c8f829cdd1631ec90e8fae5b4d8063be6779e","tid":461432,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暑假搭因航CX536轉同一班機, 因為預左轉機慢慢過關, 加上之前有班支那機, 用左75分鐘<br />\n出關上2層就check in<br />\n最後仲要delay 左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中部機場一過安檢就上機, 10分鐘都唔洗到閘口</blockquote><br />\ndelay係指因航定轉果班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係後面果班"},{"pid":"1a762116af39842de7625a9e13aec2c6925aff76","tid":461432,"uid":10008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"你唔係聯程最好預一日啦，以排 UO 一delay 起碼5-6個鐘"},{"pid":"2bb2e581700ca3